data.description: Come see this 4 bedrooms 2 baths pool home located 6.4 miles from world famous Hollywood beach. This home is located to close proximity to the Hard Rock Live hotel and casino, great restaurants, world class shops, city parks, major roads and highways for easy access to get to work, the beach or any place your heart desires.    The home boast large front yard, as well as a backyard with an inground pool and deck perfect to enjoy the hot days of sunny south Florida or to entertain family and friends while enjoying a BBQ, the sun and pool.    Inside the home has tiles and wood floors, kitchen with granite counter tops, family room overlooking the pool area and much more.  Also you can easily convert this home into 2 separate living quarters to accommodate family members or otherwise.
